Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.27,0:00:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.95,0:00:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.75,0:00:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.39,0:00:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.09,0:00:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.69,0:00:06.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.45,0:00:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.12,0:00:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.68,0:00:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.51,0:00:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.14,0:00:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.79,0:00:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.05,0:00:12.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.72,0:00:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.52,0:00:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.19,0:00:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.84,0:00:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.54,0:00:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.06,0:00:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,En garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.74,0:00:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.75,0:00:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.39,0:00:26.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you've all requested, we shall have you practice practical magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For that, we brought a special teacher from the National Magic Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.68,0:00:33.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's{\fscx300}-
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.22,0:00:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.55,0:00:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Eléonore de la Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.40,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only be for a short while,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.10,0:00:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but let us all have an enjoyable training session.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.81,0:00:46.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.53,0:00:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she your sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.34,0:00:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She seems like a kind person.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.60,0:00:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How so...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&H00&\&HFFF5CA&}Like{\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&} I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like{\alpha&H00&&HFFF5CA&} I {\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&}said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I {\alpha&H00&\&HFFF5CA&}said...{\alpha&HFF&\c&HFFFFFF&}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.22,0:02:36.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Henrietta personally requested\Nmy assistance and sent me to this school.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She did?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.01,0:02:42.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, someone told the Queen that Duke Vallière's family...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.80,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...tried to lock up their youngest outcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:48.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder who was the one that said such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really wonder who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.92,0:02:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.94,0:03:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Princess came and personally asked me to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.70,0:03:03.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In person!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.00,0:03:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been told that you're doing something under the Princess' secret orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.53,0:03:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What can you possibly be doing when you can't even use average magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.23,0:03:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.46,0:03:16.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget it. I bet it's nothing special, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.33,0:03:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's a great opportunity, so I will watch over you from today onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that strange things won't latch onto you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.83,0:03:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.62,0:03:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-neesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.28,0:03:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're here, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.43,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, as Eléonore-neesama's assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.02,0:03:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's got a weak body, so she'd be better off staying home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I want to be by Louise's side no matter what", she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.06,0:03:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm delighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be reassuring to have you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:04:00.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, "to have both of you around", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.10,0:04:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Both of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.15,0:04:03.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.68,0:04:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do all of the Duke's daughters really wear ones like these?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.04,0:04:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.79,0:04:17.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.76,0:04:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.13,0:04:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise's sister told me to unpack her luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.12,0:04:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I spotted a lingerie burglar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.45,0:04:27.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding, right...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.95,0:04:32.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave this kind of thing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.18,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.21,0:04:35.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, they're so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.19,0:04:39.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could wear something like these, even if it's only once,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.47,0:04:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but they probably wouldn't suit me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.37,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you'd look fine in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.70,0:04:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.82,0:04:50.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,may I try them on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah. Please go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to wear ones like these,\NI wouldn't be inferior to Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.09,0:05:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you're changing {\i1}here{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.48,0:05:03.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How long is Saito going to take?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Louise, y-you got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:12.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta's only helping me organise the clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.15,0:05:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I only wanted to please Saito-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san, you don't have to play dumb.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I won't forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.12,0:05:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You swore to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.98,0:05:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even kissed me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you got it all wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.79,0:05:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.72,0:05:35.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...lying dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.36,0:05:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it have been from the Principal's office?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.45,0:05:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, let's go take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.31,0:05:45.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.99,0:05:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.84,0:05:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Colbert-sensei, what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.07,0:05:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I just got here myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It appears that a ruffian broke into the Principal's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, everybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was only a minor incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.18,0:06:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody, return to your rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:06.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, Old Osmond!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.52,0:06:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you not hear me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.06,0:06:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I ordered you all to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.42,0:06:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Musketeer Force will investigate the cause of the explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:18.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.44,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have you give me a good explanation of what happened before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Saito. We must talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:26.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's related to our mission. I want to borrow Saito's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, but I'd like you to stand by in your room.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.31,0:06:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.83,0:06:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stand by in your room, Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.83,0:06:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.40,0:06:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ruffian broke in while I was gone and destroyed this safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, my familiar was watching as the events unfolded, so it came to get me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.05,0:06:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Motsognir?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.01,0:06:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.10,0:06:59.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're huge!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.33,0:07:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was very nimble, so she got away in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.56,0:07:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was inside the safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.93,0:07:26.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wind Ruby and the Water Ruby.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.13,0:07:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Queen Henrietta told me to hold onto them the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.04,0:07:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said that they were precious items to her, but were too much of a pain to keep them close by.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.77,0:07:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fortunately, the ones stolen were imitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.48,0:07:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Imitations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.98,0:07:44.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real ones aren't kept here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.35,0:07:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I forwarded them to my friend in Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.07,0:07:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right to give Her Highness' precious items to a foreigner?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.14,0:07:58.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safer than keeping them at the palace or at this academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.36,0:08:04.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There were no signs of anybody\Nescaping from or entering the campus.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.92,0:08:06.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the ruffian is...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.61,0:08:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...an insider.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.89,0:08:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.88,0:08:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, I'd like Chesaré-dono and Saito to help find the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.08,0:08:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind that, but what about Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.00,0:08:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's she on standby?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.43,0:08:25.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The culprit used Earth magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.00,0:08:29.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, all of the mages are suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.51,0:08:30.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.46,0:08:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise can't use such advanced magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We are not suspecting Miss Vallière.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.46,0:08:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, the two who arrived recently are a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.01,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear that Duke Vallière is against the Queen's doctrine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.28,0:08:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be trying to use the Wind Ruby and Water Ruby...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...as proof of a scandal, and employ that as an excuse to overthrow the Queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.12,0:08:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:01.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really suspecting Louise's sisters?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.08,0:09:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All mages are suspects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.81,0:09:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make a list of the ones who can use Earth magic and investigate thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.25,0:09:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chesaré-dono and I shall handle the females.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.77,0:09:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michel and Saito, you two handle the teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.30,0:09:18.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... how do we check?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.04,0:09:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This seal is a magic item only I can use.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.45,0:09:27.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once applied, even a Triangle Mage cannot erase its effects.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.85,0:09:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.61,0:09:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seal is pressed here on the ruffian's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.83,0:09:33.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:38.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how are we doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.48,0:09:40.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going to tell them to show us their chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.07,0:09:45.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave the Vallière sisters to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.29,0:09:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll handle the other teachers.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.38,0:09:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Aren't we working together?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Work with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say that again after you improve your swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.40,0:09:57.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll only be dragging me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay out of my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.93,0:10:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so uncute. {sounds like he's sarcastically calling her cute}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'll sneak in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.49,0:10:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Good evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.06,0:10:13.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.86,0:10:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.89,0:10:24.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's wearing some pretty cute pyjamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.93,0:10:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now, excuse me for a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.61,0:10:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm right, the seal was pressed right at the cleavage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see one at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.04,0:10:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I don't see any cleavage to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.07,0:10:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. You are pretty bold.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.26,0:10:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.44,0:10:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's... right, a physical examination!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.49,0:10:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since the flu's been spreading recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.86,0:11:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you need to say anything, say it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.99,0:11:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need to check Cattleya, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.79,0:11:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, be quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.35,0:11:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.92,0:11:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.42,0:11:38.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise? You're still awake?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.98,0:11:43.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've been searching for my familiar, since he hasn't returned yet,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.56,0:11:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and he's trying to sneak into Chii-neesama's room, of all people?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it wrong, I was only trying to sneak a peek at her chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.99,0:11:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.11,0:11:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, Chii-neesama.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to kill this dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.93,0:11:59.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.15,0:12:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pissed at myself for believing you at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.26,0:12:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd say "I love you" to anyone, wouldn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.95,0:12:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To maids, to dogs, to cats, and even to goats, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got it all wrong, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was right to have bought a new whip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.00,0:12:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take your shirt off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.78,0:12:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.56,0:12:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Saito? Your body's covered in scars.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.42,0:12:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.86,0:12:37.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went to Eléonore-oneesama's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.83,0:12:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.63,0:12:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't dare...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.41,0:12:42.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you did.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You {\i1}did{\i0} sneak into Eléonore-oneesama's room.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.90,0:12:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you can read people's minds with magic...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.54,0:12:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.69,0:12:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without using magic, I could easily read your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:13:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, can you read my mind... right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.10,0:13:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.69,0:13:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'll forgive you, Saito"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.23,0:13:07.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Saito, let's go to bed"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:10.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.35,0:13:13.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking of... {\alphaFF}killing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.31,0:13:14.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're thinking of... killing me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.69,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Save me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:22.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chii-neesama!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.84,0:13:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.85,0:13:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.61,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.88,0:13:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a burn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.00,0:13:40.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not really that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.75,0:13:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can anyone heal it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.38,0:13:45.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.60,0:13:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michel, send the onlookers away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.59,0:13:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:53.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, the ruffian appeared out of nowhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.86,0:13:59.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, the animals made noises, so I asked who it was.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.02,0:14:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How did you get the burn on your chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She melted part of the candle stand and threw a silver liquid at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.11,0:14:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alchemy... an Earth magic, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.45,0:14:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are also able to use that type of magic, am I right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.01,0:14:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.71,0:14:15.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it could've been planned and enacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.69,0:14:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.69,0:14:21.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who stood against the Principal had a seal pressed upon her chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.80,0:14:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were searching for suspects in the academy with that as the hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.23,0:14:28.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, what about her?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I came to check, but I got caught by Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:39.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Miss Cattleya figured that it'd only be a\Nmatter of time until she's checked, so she faked the assault...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to make us think that the ruffian is somebody else.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.26,0:14:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And also, to erase the seal by wounding herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.37,0:14:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how it is, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys seriously think that Chii-neesama is the one who assaulted the Principal?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, don't tell me you do, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.41,0:15:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm only cooperating with Agnes' search.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you keep it a secret from me, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.78,0:15:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my familiar, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Search or whatever, it's strange for you to do it behind my back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.63,0:15:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were suspecting Chii-neesama, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julio, did you check the other suspects?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.69,0:15:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have checked all of the girls who can use Earth magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.08,0:15:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every time either Agnes or I asked,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.18,0:15:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they all happily showed us their chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.31,0:15:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to hear the details?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.02,0:15:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.24,0:15:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, Chii-neesama would never do such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.70,0:15:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why would she?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.88,0:15:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.24,0:15:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I found these inside the hay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.75,0:15:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.95,0:15:44.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Wind Ruby and Water Ruby imitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.65,0:15:46.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.82,0:15:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.48,0:15:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Cattleya, do you admit to the charge?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.17,0:15:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:58.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have the proof in our hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be some kind of a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.80,0:16:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it has to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.30,0:16:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.56,0:16:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You stay out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Chii-neesama is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the part of the candle stand that melted and then hardened, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.41,0:16:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's either Cattleya's or the ruffian's hair.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The hair is not Cattleya's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can you be so sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.93,0:16:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, I have a potion made by my friend at the academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.51,0:16:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This hair shall now return to its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.91,0:16:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dare try to force your sister's crime onto me with your foolish magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.79,0:16:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, she's a part of this, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.78,0:16:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's arrest both of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.37,0:16:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I do not want them to think that we forced the charge on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.71,0:16:57.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, vice-captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.04,0:17:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show your chest and prove to them that you don't have the seal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.83,0:17:02.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's for the sake of the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.21,0:17:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.65,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.54,0:17:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't comply with such a humiliating order.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.81,0:17:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michel. In case the ruffian was at the site,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.21,0:17:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Principal told a lie in order to trick her.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.20,0:17:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are not imitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.46,0:17:24.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're genuine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.47,0:17:28.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you so surprised?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.06,0:17:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.47,0:17:32.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You used that lie to force the charge onto Miss Cattleya,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you thought you failed despite the trouble you went through, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.14,0:17:37.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a foolish thing you tried.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain! I am not the ruffian!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.02,0:17:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will...{\alphaFF} show you the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.45,0:17:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will... show you the proof!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.25,0:17:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Too slow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.42,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.42,0:17:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Step aside!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.90,0:17:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Michel! Stop the futile resistance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, were you suspecting me from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I respected your hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was much mystery in your background,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.08,0:18:12.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I trusted you as a swordswoman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.95,0:18:18.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if the culprit behind the incidents at the castle and today's case were the same individual,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:21.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I realised that it had to be someone close to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.48,0:18:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You could've told me, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.33,0:18:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to use a real sword, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.05,0:18:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be a loser forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.02,0:18:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:18:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's far enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.36,0:19:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the case is closed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.28,0:19:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cattleya, I'm sure you can't sleep here, so come to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.24,0:19:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Onee-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.97,0:19:12.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, you should go to bed, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.85,0:19:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time for a child to be awake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.94,0:19:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.96,0:19:20.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, Onee-sama...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.95,0:19:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm {\i0}the one who was betrayed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.16,0:19:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ten years ago, my father was a Legal Affairs Committee counsellor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.58,0:19:31.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was accused of being the leader of the graft...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.54,0:19:33.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...and had his aristocratic title taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said he was betrayed by his country and then committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.98,0:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mother followed him afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:48.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was left alone, without a place to call home, wandering about the country.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.51,0:19:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.81,0:19:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My home town was razed, and I, too, was the sole survivor.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:20:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I never held undue resentment against Her Highness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.90,0:20:02.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did she ever do for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.89,0:20:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it means borrowing Albion's power,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.96,0:20:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,unless we destroy the royal family, this country will remain rotten!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.87,0:20:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.31,0:20:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ones we must fight are the ones who monopolise this country's authority and deceive the Queen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spill it! Whose orders were you following?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.42,0:20:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An old friend of my father's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.84,0:20:25.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say any more than that.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.62,0:20:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He believed in my father's innocence,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.90,0:20:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and took me in when I was left alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.13,0:20:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lishman, the Chair President of Legal Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.52,0:20:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That case ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.77,0:20:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have solid proof, but the true leader of the graft was probably Lishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.10,0:20:49.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The one who cornered your father into death was Lishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.73,0:20:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.50,0:20:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making things up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.91,0:20:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.73,0:21:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've searched everything concerning him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because Lishman is my foe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.70,0:21:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's already morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.55,0:21:17.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to bed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.34,0:21:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.57,0:21:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you forgotten three important things?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.48,0:21:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Three?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.88,0:21:27.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you were doing something with that maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.00,0:21:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How you were helping with Agnes'\Nsearch without telling me anything.
